<div class="px-4 pt-5 my-5 text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">Digital payment</h1>
    <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
      <p class="lead mb-4">We partnered up with <a target="_blank" href="https://www.adyen.com/">Adyen</a> so that we could monetize our business model through paywalling of streams, paying directly to our artists, and more. It was initially meant to host a wallet system for our users for festival events to pay for tickets, food, and goodies.</p>
      <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center mb-5">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="overflow-hidden" style="max-height: 30vh;">
      <div class="container px-5">
        <img src="/images/portfolio-woovadyen.PNG" class="img-fluid border rounded-3 shadow-lg mb-4" alt="Example image" width="700" height="500" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<section class="page-section-background">
<div class="container py-3" id="hanging-icons">
    <h1 class="fw-bold text-center">Highlights</h1>
    <div class="row g-5 py-5">
      <div class="col-md-4 d-flex align-items-start">
        <div class="icon-square bg-light text-dark flex-shrink-0 me-3">
          <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"><use xlink:href="#toggles2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Dynamic payment system</h2>
          <p>The way we have built our platform and integration with Adyen, we could distribute money dynamically to different wallets when our users pay to watch a stream. The wallet system distributed money to Woov as a fee, to our artists, and music right organisations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 d-flex align-items-start">
        <div class="icon-square bg-light text-dark flex-shrink-0 me-3">
          <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"><use xlink:href="#cpu-fill"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Cashflow... finally!</h2>
          <p>Before this, Woov wasn't able to monetize its business model and it was solely living on initial investments. With Adyen, Woov is generating revenue and could generate data for further expansions and new investment deals.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 d-flex align-items-start">
        <div class="icon-square bg-light text-dark flex-shrink-0 me-3">
          <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"><use xlink:href="#tools"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Supporting artists</h2>
          <p>With the pandemic, artists couldn't perform and didn't had any income. With Woov, they could perform online and we enable their fanbase to support them. Woov was able to do this, because we were able to correctly calculate and payout music royalties.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="content py-5">
    <h1 class="text-center">Interested in my work or what I could do for you?</h1>
    <h2 class="pb-3 text-center">Lets get in touch and leave a message.</h2>
    <div class="container text-center contact-form">
      <form class="p-5 border rounded-3 bg-light" action="https://formspree.io/f/xzbydwrk" method="POST">
        <div class="mb-3 text-start">
          <label class="pb-2" for="floatingInput"> Your email address</label>
          <input name="_replyto" type="email" class="form-control" id="floatingInput" placeholder="johnwick@continental.com">
        </div>
        <div class="mb-3 text-start">
          <label class="form-label" id="floatingInput">Your message</label>
          <textarea name="message" class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlTextarea1" rows="3" placeholder="My dog has gone missing. Where can I find my dog?"></textarea>
        </div>
        <button class="w-100 btn btn-lg btn-primary page-section-background2" type="submit">Send it!</button>
      </form>
            
</section>


